{
  "stem": "13833.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So thanks God, the last minute, the boy was sent to England.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And our [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hess ?] survived the whole war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after the war, of course, the family went back and helped her a lot and helped because she would not leave.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there were a few marvelous people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Also, her lawyer kept all her money, a Christian, every penny.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So after that, they found her here in America.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they called her and said that I tripled your money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- So--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--so there were-- but I, I didn't feel anything right then.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not quite.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Hungary, at this point, in '38.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went, then, to-- no, it was still '37, '37.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I started to learn Montessori at Montessori School.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in '37, then, I was invited to Rome to learn from Mother Montessori herself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I spent a whole Rome-- a whole year in Rome, where, again, you didn't hear any differences.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was exciting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, when I came back, then I went direct-- always, we went a little bit to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because we had a-- we have a very big family there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I went then to England.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I have been in England for a year.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I came back again and spent part of '39 home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I went three months before September-- [LAUGHS] I was back in Geneva.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was the time when Franco already took over Spain.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's when I begin to realize what war can do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The whole Prado-- I don't know how many of you ever been in Spain.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The Prado was brought down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The whole walls, they took out and put it up in Geneva.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
